original_title: Joe Lycett: That's the Way, A-Ha, A-Ha, Joe Lycett
overview: Live stand-up performance by English comedian Joe Lycett, recorded in May 2016 at The Duchess Theatre in London. The show includes the Birmingham comic's mischievous views on sexuality, politics and celebrity culture.
title: Joe Lycett: That's the Way, A-Ha, A-Ha, Joe Lycett
